abc  ¦  1  𝄀
abc  ¦  2  𝄀
aabb  ¦  6
select sum(a),group_concat(distinct b,c separator '|') from t1 group by a;
➤ sum(a)[-5,64,0]  ¦  group_concat(distinct b, c, |)[12,0,0]  𝄀
1  ¦  abc  𝄀
